<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="28" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[812,1451,256,440]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[812,936,256,281]" pageId="5" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[812,910,257,281]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="28">Remarks</emphasis>
. –
</emphasis>
This species is very similar to 
<emphasis box="[1263,1279,257,280]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="28">P</emphasis>
